{"tid":2478633,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk弟弟再次沽出Tesla股份 獲利愈七百萬美元","createTime":"2021-04-07T08:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:15:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"59d75bb88214deaff1121d21b4597bbecfea9cda","tid":2478633,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕伊隆&middot;馬斯克（Elon Musk）的弟弟金巴爾（Kimbal Musk），也是特斯拉的董事之一，他在本週美國證券交易委員會（SEC）上的申報文件上顯示，他4月時高賣了一些特斯拉股份，大賺722萬美元（約新台幣2.05億元）。<br />\n<br />\n《Marketwatch》報導，文件顯示金巴爾本月1日行使股票選擇權，以每股74.17美元買入1.2萬股普通股，價值89萬美元（約新台幣2531.6萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉表示，股票銷售是金巴爾2020年5月19日通過的交易計劃的一部分。賣出這1.2萬股後，金巴爾仍持有59萬9740股特斯拉普通股，目前價值約4.147億美元，並持有19萬7250股的認股權。<br />\n<br />\n而金巴爾似乎眼光頗準，一見到特斯拉高點就賣，他前1次售股是在2月9日，當天特斯拉報849.46美元，1週過後便開始下跌，至今仍未站回800美元關卡；更前1次則是在去年9月1日，當時前1天為特斯拉的歷史高位，回落後過了2個半月才越過此高點。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/ec.ltn.com.tw/amp/article/breakingnews/3492075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3492075&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=08b1367c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/ec.ltn.com.tw/amp/article/breakingnews/3492075</a>"},{"pid":"ddb3a547cc7cdf893fd148f5c197458578fc4f69","tid":2478633,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"short call 姐"},{"pid":"7c5e5f0873da403c234fd4f8f044b2f647beee75","tid":2478633,"uid":300630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:18:40.000Z","msg":"有錢你唔用？"},{"pid":"af49fbaabbda935ac7a81dcdc9a19ddf20e468a0","tid":2478633,"uid":316744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"咁少炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔用牛牛貼倉一日都唔止賺咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ad72d03621708309e94b18facdbfa291f8acbd","tid":2478633,"uid":30070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"提款機"},{"pid":"e74b174e8b4119bf1a5d53399565d88b627662f9","tid":2478633,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"屌佢老弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914d66d7bb563e0c47908bfa29e2135910f09ce8","tid":2478633,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"墨屎叔叔"},{"pid":"6ee2b20faf9d31b1a11c735833f35e0a2fa3cf29","tid":2478633,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"賣1.2萬股 仲有59萬幾股"}]}